<A HREF=http://www.eng.usyd.edu.au/~bernardg>BJG</A> - 
<A HREF=mailto:B.Gardner@eng.usyd.edu.au>B.Gardner@eng.usyd.edu.au</A><BR>
Jenny Astridge -
<A HREF=mailto:J.Astridge@library.usyd.edu.au>J.Astridge@library.usyd.edu.au</A>
</ADDRESS>
