<H1>The Engineering Faculty's WWW server</H1>
<BODY>
This server is running on netserv.eng.usyd.edu.au, a
DECSystem 3100 with 24Mb of RAM and 2Gb of disk. netserv sits on
<A HREF=/~bernardg/desk>Bernard's desk</A>, next to
<A HREF=http://marvin.faceng.su.oz.au/about.html>marvin</A> and acts as
a general network server for the Engineering Faculty.
