<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">

<Center><b><font size=5>The Lean for Life Foundation</center></B></FONT><hr>

<font size=4><Blockquote><Blockquote><Blockquote>The mission of Lindora's Lean for Life Foundation is threefold: <p>to provide obesity research support and funding; <p>to conduct a public education campaign about obesity, especially in the area of prevention; <p>and to assist financially-compromised obese patients in gaining access to treatment.
</DOC>
