<title> UTME Academic Staff </title>
<h1> F.P.J. Rimrott</h1>
<img src="../photos/rimrott.gif">
<h4>Dipl.Ing. (Karlsruhe), M.A.Sc., Ph.D. (Penn State), Dr.Ing. (Darmstadt), <br>
