<DOCOLDNO>IA066-000398-B033-128</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://me.me.utoronto.ca:80/openhouse/openhouse.html 128.100.49.1 19970112191658 text/html 11393
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
