http://www.cec.sped.org:80/ab/student.htm 204.168.19.228 19970101070732 text/html 124963
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Wednesday, 01-Jan-97 07:07:26 GMT
