<TABLE WIDTH=475 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0>  
<TR><td width=60></td><TD ALIGN=left WIDTH=315><H2> Digests, Fact Sheets, Minibibs </H2> </TD></TR>   </TABLE>  </center> 

<TABLE WIDTH=510 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0>  
<TR><td width=60></td><TD WIDTH=450 ALIGN=LEFT>  <B><I><a href=gopher://ericir.syr.edu:70/11/Clearinghouses/16houses/ERIC_EC>Digests
</A></b></I>.  ERIC digests are short reports (1,500 to 2,000 words) that provide a basic overview, plus pertinent references, on topics of interest to the broad educational community.  ERIC digests are in the public domain and may be freely duplicated.<BR> 

<B><I><BR>Fact Sheets</a></B></I><P> 
<ul>
<IMG SRC="/ericec/new.gif" ALT=New Item ALIGN=right>
<li><a href="/fact/grants.htm">Grants/Funding Information</a>
