<li><a href="/fact/gt-stdir.htm"> State Directors of Programs for the Gifted</a>
<li> <a href="/fact/internat.htm"> International/National Associations for Gifted Education</a>
<li> <a href="/fact/stateadv.htm"> State Associations for the Gifted</a>
<li><a href=gopher://ericir.syr.edu:70/00/Clearinghouses/16houses/ERIC_EC/Instruction_Management/E735> Planning Accessible Conferences and Meetings</a>



</ul>

<strong><I>Minibibs</i></strong>.  Minibibliographies (or "minibibs") contain annotated readings on a particular topic.  In some cases, the "Readings" may be combined with "Resources" on a specific topic.</a></B></I><P>

<ul>
<li><a href="/faq/add-read.htm">Readings and Resources on Attention Deficit Disorder (ADD)/Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorders (ADHD)</a><br>
