<STRONG>For CEC Units</STRONG><p>

The application process for Awards for CEC Units begins in June and concludes September 1 each year. Application instructions and materials will be posted here in June 1997. If you have any questions, please contact Cheryl Racey, Membership Programs, at <A HREF="mailto:cherylr@cec.sped.org">cherylr@cec.sped.org</A> or by calling 1-800-845-6232.<p>

