<TR>  
<TD WIDTH=475 ALIGN=LEFT>  




CEC's annual convention provides the kind of exposure to special education
practitioners that publishers and 
manufacturers really need to sell products. <BR> 
 <BR> 
<B><I>Convention Dates</B></I><BR>
<table border=0>
