<TR>  
<h2>Subscription Information</H2>  
</TD>  
</TR>  
</TABLE>
</center> 


<I>TEACHING Exceptional Children</I> is published 6 times per year (Sept/Oct,
Nov/Dec, Jan/Feb, March/April, May/June, and July/Aug) by The Council for
Exceptional Children (CEC), 1920 Association Drive, Reston, Virginia 20191-1589. All
members receive <I>TEACHING Exceptional Children</I> as part of their membership
package.<P>

Subscriptions to <I>TEACHING Exceptional Children</I> are available without
membership to CEC.<P>

U.S., $58 per year<br>
Foreign-Surface, $66 per year<br>
Foreign-Air Printed Matter, $95 per year<br>
Single copy price is $10. <P>

Please call <B>1-800-232-7323</B> and CEC will gladly take your order.

