http://www.cec.sped.org:80/pp/discip2.htm 204.168.19.228 19970101073201 text/html 12412
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Wednesday, 01-Jan-97 07:32:10 GMT
